defs.docs: Wrappers for total order on Floats.

defs.name: NotNaN
defs.docs:
A wrapper around Floats providing an implementation of Ord and Hash.

 A NaN value cannot be stored in this type.

defs.name: FloatIsNaN
defs.docs: An error indicating an attempt to construct NotNan from a NaN

defs.name: OrderedFloat
defs.docs:
A wrapper around Floats providing an implementation of Ord and Hash.

 NaN is sorted as *greater* than all other values and *equal*
 to itself, in contradiction with the IEEE standard.

defs.name: unchecked_new
